37344>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37344>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37345>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37346>>>    End_Procedure
37347>>>    
37347>>>End_Object
