38352>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
38355>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38355>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38355>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38355>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38355>>>>>
38355>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38356>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38357>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38358>>>>>
38358>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38358>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38359>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38360>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
38361>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
38362>>>>>
38362>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
38364>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
38365>>>>>        End
38365>>>>>>
38365>>>>>        Else Begin
38366>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38367>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38368>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38369>>>>>        End
38369>>>>>>
38369>>>>>    End_Procedure
