38999>>>>>        End
38999>>>>>>
38999>>>>>        Else Begin
39000>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
39001>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
39002>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
39003>>>>>        End
39003>>>>>>
39003>>>>>    End_Procedure
